ra]]\n| align=\"right\" | Mariano Morett\n| align=\"right\" | 70,000\n| align=\"right\" | 1,252\n| align=\"right\" | 175.71\n|- \n| III\n| [[La Laguna Department|La Laguna]]\n| align=\"right\" | 47,000\n|  align=\"right\" | [[Playa del Carmen|El Carmen]]\n| align=\"right\" | Manuel Maria Sandoval\n| align=\"right\" | 5,000\n| align=\"right\" | 1,685\n| align=\"right\" | 27.89\n|- \n| XXXIX\n| [[Mapim\u00ed Department|Mapim\u00ed]]\n| align=\"right\" | 6,777\n|  align=\"right\" | [[Zaragoza Municipality, Coahuila|San Fernando de Rosas]]\n| align=\"right\" |\n| align=\"right\" | 1,000\n| align=\"right\" | 4,528\n| align=\"right\" | 1.50\n|- \n| XXXVI\n| [[Matamoros Department|Matamoros]]\n| align=\"right\" | 41,000\n|  align=\"right\" | [[Matamoros]]\n| align=\"right\" | Pedro J. de la Garza\n| align=\"right\" | 41,000\n| align=\"right\" | 2,195\n| align=\"right\" | 18.68\n|- \n| XXXIV\n| [[Matehuala Department|Matehuala]]\n| align=\"right\" | 82,427\n|  align=\"right\" | [[Matehuala]]\n| align=\"right\" |\n| align=\"right\" | 3,500\n| align=\"right\" | 2,097\n| align=\"right\" | 39.31\n|- \n| XL\n| [[Mazatl\u00e1n Department|Mazatl\u00e1n]]\n| align=\"right\" | 94,387\n|  align=\"right\" | [[Mazatl\u00e1n]]\n| align=\"right\" | Gregorio Almeda\n| align=\"right\" | 15,000\n| align=\"right\" | 2,116\n| align=\"right\" | 44.61\n|- \n| XXII\n| [[Michoac\u00e1n Department|Michoac\u00e1n]]\n| align=\"right\" | 417,378\n|  align=\"right\" | [[Morelia]]\n| align=\"right\" | Ramon Mendez\n| align=\"right\" | 25,000\n| align=\"right\" | 1,750\n| align=\"right\" | 238.5\n|- \n| XXVIII\n| [[Nayarit Department|Nayarit]]\n| align=\"right\" | 78,605\n|  align=\"right\" | [[Acaponeta]]\n| align=\"right\" | Manuel Rivas\n| align=\"right\" | 2,000\n| align=\"right\" | 1,718\n| align=\"right\" | 45.75\n|- \n| XLIII\n| [[Nazas Department|Nazas]]\n| align=\"right\" | 46,495\n|  align=\"right\" | Inde\u00e9\n| align=\"right\" |\n| align=\"right\" | 5,000\n| align=\"right\" | 3,089\n| alig